Revision history for Net-Async-Zitadel

{{$NEXT}}

  - Initial release
  - Async OIDC client: discovery, JWKS, token verification, userinfo, introspection, token endpoint
  - Async Management API: users, projects, apps, service users, machine keys, metadata, orgs
  - TTL-based caching for discovery (1h) and JWKS (5min), configurable
  - JWKS in-flight coalescing to prevent concurrent refresh race conditions
  - Structured exception hierarchy (Net::Async::Zitadel::Error)
